{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4a5d6d99f4","title":"（并冈山）土地法","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ed6e300829","index":0,"year":1928,"month":12,"day":null,"articleId":"4a5d6d99f4"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji4-1","name":"毛泽东全集第4卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji4-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji4-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"24e13efd6a","type":"paragraph","text":"（并冈山）土地法","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4a5d6d99f4"},{"id":"6f955a7a41","type":"paragraph","text":"（1928年12月）一、没收一切土地归苏维埃政府所有，用下列三种方法分配之：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4a5d6d99f4"},{"id":"49a85bc8d6","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）分配农民个别耕种：（二）分配农民共同耕种：（三）由苏维埃政府组织模范农场耕种，","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4a5d6d99f4"},{"id":"8788cc81b2","type":"paragraph","text":"以上三种方法，以第一种为主体。遇特别情形，或苏维埃政府有力时，兼用二三两种","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4a5d6d99f4"},{"id":"e21e9c67b0","type":"paragraph","text":"二、一切土地，经苏维埃政府没收并分配后，禁止买卖。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4a5d6d99f4"},{"id":"62afeede40","type":"paragraph","text":"三、分配土地之后，除老幼疾病没有耕种能力及服公众勤务者以外，其余的人均须强制劳动。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4a5d6d99f4"},{"id":"f19543b9ce","type":"paragraph","text":"四、分配土地的数量标准：","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4a5d6d99f4"},{"id":"11a727c8db","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）以人口为标准，男女老幼平均分配。（二）以劳动力为标准，能劳动者比不能劳动者多分士地一倍。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4a5d6d99f4"},{"id":"d5085fdf63","type":"paragraph","text":"以上两个标准，以第一个为主体。看特殊情形的地方，得适用第二个标准。采取第一个标准的理由：","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4a5d6d99f4"},{"id":"d7324c7549","type":"paragraph","text":"（中）在养老育婴的设备未完备以前，老幼如分田过少，必至不能维持生活。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4a5d6d99f4"},{"id":"62d767ddd6","type":"paragraph","text":"（乙）以人口为标准计算分田，比较简单方便。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4a5d6d99f4"},{"id":"e1a983c193","type":"paragraph","text":"（丙）没有老小的人家很少。同时老小虽无耕种能力，但在分得田地后，政府亦得分配以相当之公众勤务，如任交通等。五、分配土地的区域标准：","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4a5d6d99f4"},{"id":"c3d7f487dd","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）以乡为单位分配。（二）以几乡为单位分配（如永新之小江区）。（三）以区为单位分配（如逐川之黄增区）。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4a5d6d99f4"},{"id":"29827dc429","type":"paragraph","text":"以上三种标准，以第一种为主体。遇特别情形时，得适用第二第三两种标准。","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4a5d6d99f4"},{"id":"5d282ff055","type":"paragraph","text":"六、山林分配法：","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4a5d6d99f4"},{"id":"e566e2f041","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）茶山”、柴山，照分田的办法，以乡为单位，平均分配耕种使用。","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4a5d6d99f4"},{"id":"15fd85b7fd","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）竹木山，归苏维埃政府所有。但农民经苏维埃政府许可后，得享用竹木。竹木在五十根以下，须得乡苏维埃政府许可。百根以下，须得区苏维埃政府许可。百根以上，须得县苏维埃政府许可。","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4a5d6d99f4"},{"id":"4f5ed4a9ed","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）竹木概由县苏维埃政府出卖，所得之钱，由高级苏维埃政府支配之。","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4a5d6d99f4"},{"id":"257da9e417","type":"paragraph","text":"七、土地税之征收：","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4a5d6d99f4"},{"id":"dc16cb15fe","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）土地税依照生产情形分为三种：1.百分之十五；2.百分之十；3.百分之五","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4a5d6d99f4"},{"id":"ae46228a1d","type":"paragraph","text":"以上三种方法，以第一种为主体。遇特别情形，经高级苏维埃政府批准，得分别适用二三两种。","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4a5d6d99f4"},{"id":"2664f03ce1","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）如遇天灾或其他特殊情形时，得呈明高级苏维埃政府核准，免纳土地税","index":21,"publicati